kg.com/thread/435231</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據二：五毛擾亂視聽妖言惑眾</ins><br />\nJR：(人手置頂) 屈毛黨名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/405731\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/405731</a><br />\nRedBaron：關愛座呢隻五毛都算高招<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451674\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451674</a><br />\nGladiclus：（大踢爆）關愛座hunter係5毛！被bam屈毛派親身指證！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451720\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451720</a><br />\nJR：要求admin立即ban左三位會員︰關愛座hunter, 濕鳩塞鷗, 1000歲人瑞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451747\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451747</a><br />\nRedBaron（已改名）：香港獨立之後一定要實行獨裁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/452801\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/452801</a><br />\n極右派政治家：關愛座底已起, 電話號碼流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/457077\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/457077</a></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a15cf4ef5f06e8cf6c428b864428924ce2b1becd","tid":459780,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T05:33:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14905821f37f9c9dbb6bd63bd8fd399b3dc91ce1","tid":459780,"uid":9581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T06:35:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌狗泥真心愛國的</blockquote><br />\n要求你刪除有關屌狗既字眼"},{"pid":"843f2462e6b8cf1840a4df0912657310f1cb7be1","tid":459780,"uid":9581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T11:04:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬的而且確係5毛</blockquote><br />\n真愛國"},{"pid":"f479cbabee890e8b8489024403e2725e8fbacd23","tid":459780,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T11:09:05.000Z","msg":"樓主改名五毛<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/190858_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F190858_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=7a28d062&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"